<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">وتأسَّنَ عهدُه:</span> إِذا تغيَّر.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>و <span class="c4">[تَأَسَّى]</span>: إِذا تعزَّى.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
